      @NotNull public static @NotNull Nutrition register​(@NotNull @NotNull org.bukkit.NamespacedKey key, @NotNull @NotNull org.bukkit.inventory.ItemStack itemStack, int carbs, int proteins, int vitamins)
      Register a new Nutrition

      The plugin will check if the item matches (with the exception for stack size) and apply the appropriate nutrients to the player

      Parameters:
      key - NamespacedKey to register
      itemStack - Itemstack to register
      carbs - Carb value for this Nutrition
      proteins - Protein value for this Nutrition
      vitamins - Vitamin value for this Nutrition
      Returns:
      Newly registered nutrition
